application_type_full: Prior Approval: Change of use - offices to dwellinghouses
description: Application for determination as to whether the prior approval of the local planning authority is required for the change of use of property from offices (Use Class B1a) to 98 self contained flats, comprising of 9 x Studio flats, 79 x 1 bed and 10 x 2 bed flats. (Use Class C3), under Part 3 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development Order) 1995 (as amended).
